Class SynthSpinnerUI.SpinnerLayout

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.plaf.synth.SynthSpinnerUI.SpinnerLayout
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LayoutManager, UIResource
    Enclosing class:
    SynthSpinnerUI

    private static class SynthSpinnerUI.SpinnerLayout
extends Object
implements LayoutManager, UIResource
    A simple layout manager for the editor and the next/previous buttons. See the SynthSpinnerUI javadoc for more information about exactly how the components are arranged.
